[
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "label": "Paragraph",
    "content": "Forgoing her usual colour-blocked dresses and vibrant ensembles for yet another official state occasion, First Lady **[Melania Trump](http://www.harpersbazaar.com.au/celebrity/melania-trump-style-file-12390|target=\"_blank\")** has once again stepped out of the political fashion-box—this time in a chic grey suit.\n\nFor a meeting with Prime Minister **[Justin Trudeau](http://www.harpersbazaar.com.au/celebrity/justin-trudeau-kissing-his-wife-13568|target=\"_blank\")** and his wife, **Sophie Gregoire Trudeau**, at the White House on Wednesday, the First Lady picked a gunmetal-grey pinstriped **Ralph Lauren Collection** suit, consisting of a pair of wide-legged pants and a fitted blazer."
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "label": "Image",
    "content": {
      "source": "",
      "credits": [],
      "tags": [],
      "url": "http://d3lp4xedbqa8a5.cloudfront.net/s3/digital-cougar-assets/hb/2017/10/12/1507767863722_GettyImages-860241630.jpg",
      "valid": true
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "label": "Paragraph",
    "content": "She accessorised her look with a crisp white button up, done all the way to the top—very *Annie Hall*—and an undone black scarf tie. Later photos reveal she also wore black pointed pumps (although in this instance they are less likely to cause scandal, than in her recent [outings](http://www.harpersbazaar.com.au/fashion/melania-trump-puerto-rico-heels-controversy-14558|target=\"_blank\"))."
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "label": "Image",
    "content": {
      "source": "",
      "credits": [],
      "tags": [],
      "url": "http://d3lp4xedbqa8a5.cloudfront.net/s3/digital-cougar-assets/hb/2017/10/12/1507767857677_GettyImages-860242294.jpg",
      "valid": true
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "label": "Paragraph",
    "content": "Her signature flicked blow-out, and smoky eye were in place, as ever."
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "label": "Image",
    "content": {
      "source": "",
      "credits": [],
      "tags": [],
      "url": "http://d3lp4xedbqa8a5.cloudfront.net/s3/digital-cougar-assets/hb/2017/10/12/1507767874935_GettyImages-860241632.jpg",
      "valid": true
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "label": "Paragraph",
    "content": "This isn’t the first time the First Lady has donned a suit, however. Although she is fond of skirt-suits (her fire-engine red Dior ensemble in Paris was a prime example), Trump has donned a full blazer-and-pants combo twice before. \n\nOnce in a white Dolce & Gabbana suit with a black shirt, and another time in grey Ralph Lauren Collection."
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "label": "Image",
    "content": {
      "source": "",
      "credits": [],
      "tags": [],
      "url": "http://d3lp4xedbqa8a5.cloudfront.net/s3/digital-cougar-assets/hb/2017/10/12/1507767891547_GettyImages-686317784.jpg",
      "valid": true,
      "caption": "Wearing Dolce & Gabbana in Saudi Arabia."
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "label": "Image",
    "content": {
      "source": "",
      "credits": [],
      "tags": [],
      "url": "http://d3lp4xedbqa8a5.cloudfront.net/s3/digital-cougar-assets/hb/2017/10/12/1507767934486_GettyImages-849533968.jpg",
      "valid": true,
      "caption": "Wearing Ralph Lauren Collection at the UN General Assembly."
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "label": "Paragraph",
    "content": "Both times she forwent a tie."
  }
]
